.os.slash:{[p] };

/F/ returns a command that can be used to find old files
/P/ dir:SYMBOL - directory to look into
/P/ age:LONG - age of the files in days
/P/ pattern:SYMBOL - pattern for the file path
.os.find:{[dir;age;pattern] };

